cool and relaxed,

00:26:22.120 --> 00:26:24.600 align:middle line:84%
and be ready to protest
in a relaxed way.

00:26:24.600 --> 00:26:27.250 align:middle line:84%
Recognize the causes that are
in alignment with what we want,

00:26:27.250 --> 00:26:28.850 align:middle line:90%
and so that we can coalesce.

00:26:28.850 --> 00:26:31.850 align:middle line:84%
Not get all bogged down in the
same egotistical pitfalls that

00:26:31.850 --> 00:26:34.530 align:middle line:84%
have befell our great
heroes of the '60s.

00:26:34.530 --> 00:26:36.225 align:middle line:84%
